snippet.title: Triple Agent! - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Triple Agent! is a mobile party game about deception and espionage for 5 or more players. All you need to play is a single mobile device and a few friends. Each game is an intense 10 minutes of deception, cunning, and deduction.

www.triple-agent.com

App Store link:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/triple-agent/id1247445624?ls=1&mt=8

Play Store link:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tastyrook.agent
